[" God's Rebuke now slows movement speed of hit enemies by 40% for 1.5 seconds.", ' Bulwark can now be toggled.
When toggled on, Mars gets disarmed, has his movement speed slowed by 20%, and gets his facing direction locked.
While toggled on, any enemy attack projectile launched on an ally while within 800 range of Mars, and within the Bulwark angles, has a 70% chance to get redirected to Mars instead.
While toggled on, Mars does require turning to move, cast spells or use items.', 'When toggled on, Mars gets disarmed, has his movement speed slowed by 20%, and gets his facing direction locked.', 'While toggled on, any enemy attack projectile launched on an ally while within 800 range of Mars, and within the Bulwark angles, has a 70% chance to get redirected to Mars instead.', 'While toggled on, Mars does require turning to move, cast spells or use items.', "Changed  Arena Of Blood tree destruction radius to match the arena's radius, instead of a fixed 100 radius."]
